{"to":["nurse.thompson@pinegrove.edu"],"subject":"Timmy – Health & Vaccination Update","body":"Hello Mrs. Thompson,

I hope you’re doing well. I’m writing to provide the requested update for Timmy’s student health file.

– Current Health Status: Timmy is in good overall health and has no restrictions on school attendance or activities at this time.
– Vaccination Status: Timmy is fully compliant with the routine pediatric immunization schedule and has no outstanding doses.

If you need any further documentation or have additional questions, please let me know and I’ll be happy to assist.

Kind regards,
Dr. Jane
Pediatrician, Happy Valley Children’s Clinic"}
